text: Þonon up on tælen oð blindan wylle.
Þanon on otrig on stræt pol.
Ðanon suð andlang dune on wyrtrum oð wicgincland.
Of ðare landscore oð waccas treow.
Þonne on otrig, at þam borstan clife.
Þonne norð on hearpað eft on stræt geat.
Her is seo land scoru wicginc Landes & otrig Landes.
Ærest of landscor hege on land scor broc.
Ðanon on otrig & þonne adun on stream oð rean clif.
Þanon oð hæð pen suþewardne on þone holan stoc.
Þanon on bigulfes burh suþewarde of bigulfes borh on setl þorn.
Þanon on blacan dune norðeanwearde on herpoð to street gete.
